."],[2352,2498,"So you either go out there right now,"],[2540,2660,"or you die now."],[2694,2786,"Your choice."],[3048,3174,"Oh my God!"],[3224,3347,"Where's this location?"],[3347,3478,"What is this place?"],[3511,3574,"Get out the way."],[3574,3645,"Postal boy."],[3699,3807,"I'm sorry, boss."],[3820,3924,"I'm just looking for my wife,"],[3953,4041,"Isabella."],[4066,4158,"Have you seen her?"],[4341,4450,"Hey, take it easy. I'm-"],[4617,4671,"Well then,"],[4738,4864,"ask Bianca to come out."],[4867,4957,"That's right."],[5013,5180,"Unless the dead can rise"],[5271,5384,"or miracles happen."],[5400,5479,"Hey!"],[5555,5663,"The Morelli miracle"],[5705,5755,"is here."],[5818,5935,"If you slip up,"],[5935,6010,"we're all fucked."],[6264,6343,"Bianca?"]],"7":[[12,91,"Bianca?"],[145,300,"You still alive?"],[688,788,"Antonio Gambino."],[804,963,"Head of the Gambino family"],[971,1146,"and our sworn enemy."],[1172,1275,"Nothing would make me happier"],[1275,1413,"than this scumbag dead."],[1459,1622,"So he's Antonio?"],[1622,1764,"You wish I were dead,"],[1881,1968,"little Tony?"],[2339,2439,"Damn it!"],[2619,2736,"Donna Morelli."],[2765,2857,"You finally arrived."],[3015,3107,"That's impossible."],[3174,3303,"Bianca is supposed to be dead."],[3328,3382,"But that's her."],[3440,3495,"No."],[3495,3570,"Something's not right."],[3653,3720,"Enough!"],[3832,3953,"Stop pretending."],[3953,4041,"You're impersonating"],[4041,4200,"the boss of the Morelli family."],[4216,4259,"Antonio,"],[4259,4404,"put the fucking gun down."],[4421,4496,"You don't recognize"],[4496,4617,"the boss when you see her."],[5207,5406,"Boss, we've got an intruder on the back."],[5630,5718,"Bring him in."],[5814,5951,"-Take it easy -Hold still."],[5951,6056,"Come on, please."],[6143,6310,"Violence is not the answer."],[6310,6414,"We should be promoting"],[6414,6514,"peace and love."],[6514,6602,"Stop pretending!"],[6652,6765,"Oh, by the way,"],[6819,6973,"I got a little present for you."],[7169,7307,"Get off of me."],[7307,7357,"I'll have"],[7357,7428,"my lawyer talk to you."],[7457,7524,"Shut up!"],[7799,7932,"Antonio, what are you up to?"],[7950,8053,"Who is she?"],[8375,8458,"Who is she?"],[8733,8812,"Isabella?"]],"8":[[58,125,"Hey!"],[125,275,"Tell everybody right now."],[275,392,"Is this woman"],[392,563,"in front of us your wife?"],[692,767,"If you slip up,"],[767,888,"we're all fucked."],[888,967,"What do I do?"],[967,1071,"What do I do?"],[1368,1459,"Speak up!"],[1459,1576,"All right, take it easy."],[1626,1743,"I'll talk, alright?"],[1743,1826,"Antonio,"],[1826,1960,"you bring some random guy here"],[1960,2081,"to question her identity."],[2081,2147,"You're insane."],[2147,2256,"He's not a random."],[2381,2502,"He's her husband."],[2827,3007,"What? That's impossible!"],[3007,3078,"She's famously"],[3078,3161,"never been married."],[3303,3432,"Now you tell everyone."],[3457,3561,"Is this your wife?"],[3561,3674,"The whole West Coast"],[3674,3791,"will be mine soon."],[4054,4145,"She is..."],[4483,4579,"Pretend you don't know me"],[4579,4671,"or we're all dead."],[4692,4804,"What's going on?"],[4804,4904,"Who are they?"],[4904,5046,"Hurry up and stop stalling."],[5171,5238,"Deny it!"],[5255,5321,"Quickly!"],[5380,5492,"She is..."],[5722,5830,"Please, Simon."],[5830,5935,"Just this once."],[5935,6035,"Do the right thing."],[6114,6235,"She is not my wife."],[6235,6322,"What?"]],"9":[[8,133,"She is not my wife."],[133,225,"What?"],[280,400,"What's going on?"],[400,571,"I mean, I'm not complaining, but..."],[571,767,"We're Morse code enthusiasts."],[913,1017,"I'm gonna ask you one more time."],[1134,1226,"Is she your wife?"],[1263,1405,"Boss, you can ask me 100 times."],[1405,1547,"But she is not my wife."],[1568,1710,"What is this?"],[2206,2248,"I don't know."],[2248,2356,"She looks like my wife,"],[2423,2577,"but she is not my wife."],[2606,2694,"My housewife"],[2736,2836,"is a hopeless woman."],[2836,2932,"A coward."],[2952,3161,"She faints at the sight of blood."],[3199,3282,"This woman"],[3315,3453,"is not my wife."],[3511,3578,"Damn it! You call me"],[3578,3732,"clueless and cowardly?!"],[3732,3895,"It's just the tactic."],[3895,3949,"Damn it!"],[3949,4091,"What is going on here?"],[4091,4170,"Are you lying to me?"],[4241,4316,"I'm gonna give you"],[4316,4404,"one more chance"],[4404,4504,"to tell the truth."],[4504,4583,"And if you don't,"],[4583,4758,"I'm gonna blow your brains out."]],"10":[[112,275,"Boss, I think he passed out."],[275,429,"Then wake him up."],[1059,1247,"Bullying an innocent civilian?"],[1263,1368,"You're disgusting."],[1384,1530,"You know, Bianca's identity"],[1530,1659,"shouldn't be questioned."],[1659,1801,"Stop it with the tricks."],[1801,2027,"The Don to the Morelli Family"],[2027,2116,"is not someone"],[2116,2289,"anyone can impersonate."],[2289,2431,"And that is indeed Bianca."],[2932,2994,"Little Tony,"],[3019,3219,"this farce needs to end."],[3219,3282,"Yeah."],[3307,3395,"Why don't we talk about"],[3395,3465,"the original"],[3482,3616,"subject of this meeting."],[3724,3824,"Melville,"],[3824,3949,"I think it's all fair"],[3949,4120,"since we did most of the groundwork."],[4120,4237,"That it's ours."],[4258,4383,"But, don't worry."],[4383,4513,"Of course we'll let the other families"],[4513,4633,"do business there."],[4642,4754,"We have no objections."],[4754,4854,"Neither do we."],[4875,4984,"This is bullshit."],[5017,5109,"You have a problem?"],[5434,5526,"Nope."],[5801,5893,"Let's go."],[6506,6614,"Oh my..."],[6639,6744,"Oh God, did you..."],[6744,6831,"Did you see?"],[6898,7086,"Well done, kiddo!"],[7378,7453,"Oh shit!"],[7453,7607,"Shit, I forgot about Simon."]],"11":[[0,83,"Oh shit!"],[104,258,"Shit! I forgot about Simon."],[258,375,"We have to get him back."],[375,429,"I am telling you,"],[429,596,"that spineless man is going to betray us"],[596,725,"somehow sooner or later."],[842,971,"She's got a point."],[971,1146,"You know, Bianca will say the same thing."],[1297,1422,"I'm on it."],[2623,2715,"Morelli scum!"],[2715,2823,"Damn it!"],[3290,3528,"Oh no, come on."],[3611,3674,"Shut up!"],[3674,3812,"No, no!"],[3862,3991,"-Let me go! -Shut up!"],[3991,4079,"Come on."],[4216,4404,"What the heck, man!"],[4725,4813,"I thought you said"],[4813,4942,"Bianca was dead."],[4946,5034,"I saw her get shot"],[5034,5067,"and fall."],[5067,5213,"Then why isn't she dead?"],[5351,5422,"Get out!"],[5422,5505,"Prick!"],[5601,5676,"Someone call that"],[5676,5797,"stupid doctor in here."],[5830,5943,"I need to question him."],[6097,6151,"Boss."],[6202,6297,"That man was rescued"],[6297,6368,"by the Morelli Group."],[6410,6448,"What?"]],"12":[[33,112,"What?"],[316,417,"Useless!"],[458,554,"I knew that woman"],[554,692,"was suspicious."],[709,829,"Get a DNA sample,"],[829,959,"compare it to Bianca's."],[959,984,"Yeah?"],[1026,1113,"You want me to go?"],[1126,1217,"You want me to go?"],[1238,1284,"I'll go."],[1292,1330,"Yeah."],[1330,1372,"Of course."],[1376,1418,"Of course."],[1426,1476,"I'll go."],[2648,2748,"He's here, boss."],[3178,3353,"What did you do to him?"],[3370,3445,"He's been a little noisy,"],[3445,3520,"Wouldn't he?"],[3545,3657,"So I taped his mouth shut."],[4208,4254,"Oh, uh."],[4254,4383,"Someone get me baby oil"],[4383,4491,"and cotton swabs."],[4491,4592,"Please."],[4604,4708,"Ouch!"],[4729,4796,"A cheater"],[4796,4963,"doesn't deserve your sympathy."],[5088,5226,"Did you tell him about us?"],[5347,5430,"What the hell did you do?"],[5434,5538,"I didn't. You..."],[5538,5618,"Oh!"],[5668,5722,"Careful"],[5739,5847,"when you speak to our boss."],[5847,5914,"You understand?"],[5968,6043,"Boss?"],[6114,6227,"What the hell is going on?"],[6289,6368,"It's not your concern."],[6464,6544,"How did you even"],[6544,6631,"find this place?"],[6681,6773,"Location sharing."],[6794,6848,"Remember?"],[6898,7027,"I forgot we set that up."],[7048,7123,"I thought you getting kidnapped,"],[7123,7211,"so I got worried."],[7294,7369,"Darling,"],[7378,7469,"I haven't seen you in days."],[7469,7574,"Please come home."],[7674,7807,"Stop fucking around!"],[7841,7895,"Tell her."],[7957,8062,"Okay, fine."],[8062,8195,"I got fired because of the scandal."],[8270,8466,"So I tapped into our joint bank account."],[8495,8616,"But you had a password on it."],[8871,9008,"So you're here"],[9038,9192,"because you're broke?"],[9476,9576,"Get out!"],[9626,9751,"I never want to see you."],[9772,9834,"Actually,"],[9855,9964,"I need money"],[9964,10043,"to buy a ticket"],[10043,10130,"to get back home."],[10326,10514,"No, Isabella!"],[10564,10727,"I should buy the ticket for him."],[10848,10960,"I think you can do better."],[11048,11119,"Simon."],[11152,11257,"You're an adult."],[11269,11403,"Buy your own stupid ticket."]],"13":[[0,70,"Simon."],[104,208,"You're an adult."],[221,354,"Buy your own stupid ticket."],[500,613,"That's the spirit."],[613,734,"What's gone into you?"],[796,871,"Buy me the ticket."],[871,913,"Let's go."],[938,1005,"You know what?"],[1109,1176,"Sign this."],[1176,1276,"What is this?"],[1438,1614,"Divorce agreement. No."],[1718,1805,"No talking,"],[1889,1968,"sign it."],[2456,2640,"Quit wasting your time"],[2640,2806,"on a cheating scumbag."],[2844,2961,"Just get the divorce."],[3011,3128,"You're right."],[3148,3253,"I am done"],[3253,3349,"putting up with him."],[3349,3445,"What are you doing?"],[3691,3799,"Yeah."],[3832,3970,"That's the Donna Morelli."],[3970,4083,"She‘s done act like it."],[4083,4204,"And take him"],[4204,4350,"to the airport."],[4496,4567,"Pleasure."],[4567,4671,"What'd you do to her?"],[4671,4733,"Come on."],[4817,4917,"Why are you doing this?"],[5201,5267,"I'm not going"],[5267,5372,"with these bastards."],[5413,5509,"Oh yeah you are."],[5563,5672,"You can either go to Italy"],[5697,5809,"while all this blows over"],[5830,6056,"and enjoy some nice Sicilian hospitality"],[6093,6143,"or"],[6356,6477,"I kill you right now."],[6493,6556,"You know what,"],[6610,6740,"pasta does sound good right now."],[6758,6869,"Yeah, it does, doesn't it?"],[6990,7094,"Let's go, early guys."],[7098,7169,"I'm out of here."],[7394,7507,"Let's start a business."],[8479,8529,"Isabella,"],[8529,8637,"where are you going?"]],"14":[[33,112,"Isabella."],[258,337,"Where are you going?"],[446,579,"You know, just..."],[604,663,"You know."],[663,742,"We secured Melville,"],[767,846,"so I figured"],[846,938,"I should get on my way."],[938,1034,"You're our boss."],[1034,1130,"You can't leave."],[1167,1217,"What?"],[1363,1413,"No,"],[1413,1593,"I'm not cut out for this."],[1651,1726,"That's true."],[1926,2022,"What? I mean, to be fair,"],[2043,2177,"we can't rely on her forever."],[2193,2253,"Exactly."],[2394,2603,"And you know, he is more suitable,"],[2603,2798,"much more suitable."],[2798,2848,"Yeah."],[2907,3015,"Do a good job, kid."],[3215,3311,"You're not cut out for it"],[3311,3457,"cause you don't have Bianca's authority."],[3465,3524,"We still need her"],[3524,3628,"for the time being."],[3670,3778,"Alright, aright."],[3970,4003,"Hey."],[4029,4212,"You can't leave."],[4262,4408,"Listen, Layla."],[4446,4562,"I'm a teacher, okay?"],[4562,4662,"I... I..."],[4671,4775,"I love my students"],[4775,4924,"and I love my life, and..."],[4938,5017,"I'm not gonna"],[5034,5134,"become a gangster and..."],[5134,5313,"and live in a place full of guns."],[5338,5463,"You were born for this."],[5484,5600,"Oh, damn it."],[5600,5764,"Okay, you don't understand."],[5789,5876,"I"],[5880,5947,"am going"],[5947,6106,"to the airport, okay?"],[6973,7052,"Which way?"],[7290,7369,"-This way. -That way."],[7440,7482,"Fine."],[7503,7589,"I'll figure it out"],[7595,7665,"myself."],[7832,7912,"Isabella."],[7962,8016,"Hey."],[8241,8320,"This place is crazy."],[8320,8380,"I'm gonna get out of here"],[8380,8475,"as soon as possible."],[9651,9784,"Hey, handsome."]],"15":[[25,112,"Hey, handsome."],[379,408,"Wait!"],[462,558,"Oh shit!"],[558,625,"Bye, handsome."],[961,1010,"No, no!"],[1010,1142,"No. Please!"],[1142,1334,"No, I wanna leave."],[1365,1484,"This is kidnapping!"],[2435,2565,"Boss, are we still"],[2598,2744,"heading to the Morelli estate?"],[2802,2844,"No."],[2952,3028,"Looks like they got some"],[3028,3103,"business to handle."],[3290,3365,"Come on."],[3365,3486,"Sorry, you can't leave just yet."],[3486,3561,"Calm down."],[3561,3595,"What?"],[3616,3724,"No, no!"],[3832,3928,"No!"],[3928,4074,"Open the door."],[4166,4287,"God."],[5034,5121,"Grant."],[5188,5305,"What are you doing here?"],[5334,5447,"That woman isn't dead."],[5501,5613,"She's ruining my reputation"],[5613,5726,"as the muscle in the family."],[5759,5839,"I'm gonna kill her."],[6372,6445,"Hi."],[6498,6610,"Hey, Silvio."],[6610,6702,"Take a look at this."],[6827,6986,"Boss was killed by Antonio."],[7173,7261,"That bastard."],[7853,7932,"Perfect time."],[8662,8742,"Die!"]],"16":[[80,174,"Isabella."],[500,579,"Isabella."],[771,875,"Antonio's scum."],[1172,1226,"See?"],[1238,1343,"You can't leave us."],[1343,1476,"It's dangerous out here."],[1493,1576,"Oh my God!"],[1576,1710,"This is insane."],[1751,1789,"Listen,"],[1843,1981,"help us with one more thing."],[2022,2160,"We'll guarantee your safety."],[2160,2377,"And then whether or not you stay or not"],[2402,2494,"will be up to you."],[2556,2639,"So what's gonna happen?"],[2669,2723,"Right."],[2723,2936,"So, Bianca had an engagement"],[2936,3140,"with the head of the Romano family in Italy."],[3178,3305,"The ceremony is in a week."],[3386,3453,"So what?"],[3470,3695,"So in order to maintain our position"],[3695,3866,"as top family of the West Coast,"],[3866,4003,"we need to be on good standing"],[4003,4116,"with the Romano family."],[4141,4200,"And?"],[4283,4504,"So we need you to marry Marco."],[4521,4625,"Head of the Romano family."],[4671,4713,"What?"],[4763,4925,"Are you insane? I'm a fake."],[4925,5046,"Do you want me to die?"],[5046,5142,"You won't die."],[5142,5255,"They won't harm you."],[5263,5292,"No."],[5292,5363,"Absolutely not."],[5380,5409,"No."],[5793,587