."],[5038,5130,"Small world, huh?"]],"32":[[216,308,"What's this about?"],[371,467,"Hi."],[483,596,"The woman in the photo"],[596,679,"is from California,"],[679,850,"named Isabella Caruso."],[850,1096,"She has a husband and"],[1117,1247,"interestingly"],[1247,1472,"resembles your Lovely fiancée."],[1493,1609,"Isabella..."],[1668,1764,"Isabella?"],[1801,1926,"Yes, yes."],[1926,2056,"No, that's just my nickname."],[2168,2306,"Her name's Isabella too."],[2306,2377,"Don't tell me"],[2377,2519,"this is just a coincidence."],[2565,2640,"Come on."],[2660,2744,"I mean there's so many"],[2744,2894,"people in this world, right?"],[2894,2952,"I mean it's not"],[2952,3015,"that uncommon that"],[3015,3128,"two people look alike."],[3278,3382,"It's possible."],[3390,3474,"The photo was"],[3474,3611,"sent to me anonymously."],[3632,3691,"Someone could be"],[3691,3824,"trying to disrupt the union"],[3824,3891,"between the"],[3891,4058,"Romano and Morelli."],[4091,4183,"Fuck!"],[4183,4279,"Yes."],[4279,4462,"Yes, that must be it."],[4500,4642,"It's still a security risk"],[4642,4838,"for us that you have a look alike."],[4838,4967,"I have to be cautious"],[4967,5084,"now more than ever."],[5088,5255,"Alex, look into this."],[5271,5455,"Damn it! This man is tricky."],[5780,5918,"Enjoy your breakfast."],[6118,6177,"Sir."],[6177,6272,"Why didn't you reveal her"],[6272,6427,"true identity earlier?"],[6452,6560,"They're already engaged,"],[6577,6681,"exposing her now"],[6681,6790,"wouldn't do much."],[6790,6898,"Marco is smart."],[6898,7002,"Even if he realizes"],[7002,7161,"this Bianca is an imposter,"],[7182,7294,"it's better to have leverage, right?"],[7419,7536,"Knowledge is power."]],"33":[[371,442,"Boss."],[442,546,"Layla."],[546,759,"Luca has found my identity."],[759,821,"Okay?"],[821,930,"He even knows my name."],[930,1016,"I mean, Marco has already"],[1016,1134,"sent someone to investigate."],[1146,1217,"Alright, alright."],[1217,1267,"I'll send someone to"],[1267,1334,"take c